=Description=

"a social collaboration tool with a multi-currency system for joined value creation and accounting. Different token representing community currencies, voting rights and asset shares can be combined with standard payment solutions.

To enables participative decision making and stimulate open value creation a virtual budget can be allocated by different groups and communities to projects."
